      "description": "This is an investment-grade E46 M3 in collector condition. Under the hood, the S54B32 straight-six features a fully overhauled high-pressure Double VANOS system and synchronized individual throttle bodies, delivering a linear power band to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission shifts with mechanical precision, paired with a freshly serviced M Variable Differential Lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced and inspected for zero fatigue. The suspension retains factory kinematics with OEM bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the chassis remains taut. With documented rod bearing replacement and valve clearance adjustments, this high-revving masterpiece is mechanically flawless and cosmetically pristine.",
